[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":425},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fgit\u002F20210709\u002F1381487661\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fgit\u002F20210709\u002F1381487661\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fgit\u002F20210709\u002F1381487661\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fgit\u002F20210709\u002F1381487661\u002F":401,"related:\u002Fgit\u002F20210709\u002F1381487661\u002F":410},"\u002Fen\u002Fgit\u002F2021\u002F07\u002F09\u002Fgithub-ssh-ed25519-setup\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":383,"date":384,"description":385,"extension":386,"lang":387,"meta":388,"navigation":389,"path":390,"readingMinutes":391,"seo":392,"standalone":393,"stem":394,"tags":395,"tldr":398,"updated":398,"url":399,"__hash__":400},"content\u002FGit\u002F使用-SSH-連接-上傳到你的-GitHub-Ed25519.md","使用 SSH 連接\u002F上傳到你的 GitHub(Ed25519)","1381487661",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":374},"minimark",[11,15,31,34,37,40,43,46,55,59,62,78,81,92,102,105,116,123,133,137,140,150,153,162,165,173,180,186,189,211,214,220,224,239,245,252,258,261,267,270,276,279,290,296,299,305,309,316,322,325,328,334,341,350,353,356,370],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18,19,23,24,27,28,30],"p",{},"GitHub 除了使用 ",[20,21,22],"code",{},"https"," 模式連接\u002F上傳之外，也可以使用 ",[20,25,26],{},"ssh"," 的方式，但是 ",[20,29,26],{}," 的方式比較複雜一點，所以寫一篇紀錄一下。",[12,32,33],{"id":26},"SSH",[16,35,36],{},"前面先講點 SSH 的小知識。",[16,38,39],{},"那麼什麼是 SSH 呢？SSH 全名是「Secure Shell (安全外殼協定)」，主要是一種加密的網路傳輸協定，在早期我們的網路傳輸協定是 HTTP 模式，也就是所謂的明文傳輸，而明文傳輸就會有一些資安上的問題，例如什麼樣子的問題呢？舉例來講，明文傳輸中若中途被駭客攔截封包的話，是可以透過該封包竊取你的帳號密碼，因此就誕生了這個 SSH 協定。",[16,41,42],{},"而 SSH 主要是採用非對稱加密的方式來實施身份驗證，因此主要會有公鑰(Public key)與私鑰(Private key)這兩隻檔案，那麼什麼是非對稱加密？舉例來講對稱加密的意思就是接收方與傳送方都是使用同一個 key，而非對稱加密則是如前面所提會有公鑰與私鑰這兩隻檔案，公鑰主要用於驗證你的私鑰正確性，因此只有持有私鑰的你能夠解密或者連接哦。",[16,44,45],{},"最後總結一下重點，就是「私鑰(Private key)千萬不能外流！」只能在自己電腦上。",[16,47,48,49,54],{},"而會寫這一篇的原因主要也是與 GitHub 的政策有關，可以詳見",[50,51,53],"a",{"href":52},"\u002Fgit\u002F20210630\u002F3665920401\u002F","這篇","。",[12,56,58],{"id":57},"ssh-指令小知識","SSH 指令小知識",[16,60,61],{},"基本上你在網路找到的任何一篇 SSH key 生成的文章，大多都會寫以下這一個指令：",[63,64,69],"pre",{"className":65,"code":66,"language":67,"meta":68,"style":68},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -C \"example@example.com\"\n","cmd","",[20,70,71],{"__ignoreMap":68},[72,73,76],"span",{"class":74,"line":75},"line",1,[72,77,66],{},[16,79,80],{},"但是其實很少會提到這些關於這個指令的參數說明，因此這邊我也順便紀錄說明一下。",[16,82,83,84,87,88,91],{},"首先 ",[20,85,86],{},"ssh-keygen"," 是 SSH 服務的生成與管理等等的指令，而它後面所接著帶的 ",[20,89,90],{},"-t"," 參數意思是指要生成哪一種 key 的類型，通常比較常見的有以下兩種：",[93,94,95,99],"ul",{},[96,97,98],"li",{},"rsa (RSA加密演算法)",[96,100,101],{},"dsa (數位簽章演算法)",[16,103,104],{},"這兩種演算法是什麼就不在這篇文章內介紹內，所以可以自己上網查一下。",[16,106,107,108,111,112,115],{},"接下來是 ",[20,109,110],{},"-t rsa"," 後面的 ",[20,113,114],{},"-b"," 指令，這一個指令的意思是設定 key 的長度(bits)。",[16,117,118,119,122],{},"最後一個則是 ",[20,120,121],{},"-C"," 這個意思是新增一個註解，所以在上方指令中就是要增加一個 Email 的註解。",[16,124,125,126,128,129,132],{},"當然 ",[20,127,86],{}," 還有其他的指令，例如 ",[20,130,131],{},"-f"," 指定密鑰的生成名稱(預設是：id_rsa.pub、id_rsa)。",[12,134,136],{"id":135},"生成-ssh","生成 SSH",[16,138,139],{},"接下來示範都會以 Mac 為主，基本上 Windows 差異並不大，所以可以參考。",[16,141,142,143,149],{},"接下來就準備生成 GitHub 專用的 SSH 吧！但我們怎麼知道 GitHub 要的 SSH 是長怎樣？其實在 GitHub 官方文件這一篇「",[50,144,148],{"href":145,"rel":146},"https:\u002F\u002Fdocs.github.com\u002Fen\u002Fgithub\u002Fauthenticating-to-github\u002Fconnecting-to-github-with-ssh\u002Fgenerating-a-new-ssh-key-and-adding-it-to-the-ssh-agent",[147],"nofollow","Generating a new SSH key and adding it to the ssh-agent","」就有提到相關指令：",[16,151,152],{},"Mac",[63,154,156],{"className":65,"code":155,"language":67,"meta":68,"style":68},"ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C \"your_email@example.com\"\n",[20,157,158],{"__ignoreMap":68},[72,159,160],{"class":74,"line":75},[72,161,155],{},[16,163,164],{},"Windows",[63,166,167],{"className":65,"code":155,"language":67,"meta":68,"style":68},[20,168,169],{"__ignoreMap":68},[72,170,171],{"class":74,"line":75},[72,172,155],{},[16,174,175,176,179],{},"這時候你會發現與網路上相當多的文章都是這一個指令 ",[20,177,178],{},"ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -C \"your_email@example.com\"","，但這個指令主要是比較舊的系統不支援 Ed25519 演算法的系統所使用，而 Ed25519 雖然已經有一段時間了，但是以文獻來講安全性以及效能上會更好，因此官方建議用 Ed25519 那麼就直接用這個演算法吧。",[16,181,182],{},[183,184],"img",{"alt":86,"src":185},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F202107092325.png",[16,187,188],{},"輸入完畢後它會先問你 ssh 生成的路徑要在哪裡與是否要設置密碼：",[63,190,192],{"className":65,"code":191,"language":67,"meta":68,"style":68},"Generating public\u002Fprivate ed25519 key pair.\nEnter file in which to save the key (\u002FUsers\u002Frayxu\u002F.ssh\u002Fid_ed25519):\nEnter passphrase (empty for no passphrase):\n",[20,193,194,199,205],{"__ignoreMap":68},[72,195,196],{"class":74,"line":75},[72,197,198],{},"Generating public\u002Fprivate ed25519 key pair.\n",[72,200,202],{"class":74,"line":201},2,[72,203,204],{},"Enter file in which to save the key (\u002FUsers\u002Frayxu\u002F.ssh\u002Fid_ed25519):\n",[72,206,208],{"class":74,"line":207},3,[72,209,210],{},"Enter passphrase (empty for no passphrase):\n",[16,212,213],{},"如果沒有要特別調整的話，一直按下 Enter 即可，當你看到以下畫面時，就代表生成好了：",[16,215,216],{},[183,217],{"alt":218,"src":219},"ed25519","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F202107092329.png",[12,221,223],{"id":222},"取得-ssh-公鑰並新增到-github","取得 SSH 公鑰並新增到 GitHub",[16,225,226,227,230,231,234,235,238],{},"生成完畢後到畫面上所提示的路徑去找 SSH key，以我的電腦舉例就是在 ",[20,228,229],{},"\u002FUsers\u002Frayxu\u002F.ssh\u002F","，這邊要注意 Mac 通常預設 .ssh 資料夾是隱藏的，因此你要按下 Shift + Command + ",[20,232,233],{},".","(就是問號旁邊的 ",[20,236,237],{},">"," 按鍵)顯示隱藏資料夾就可以找到了：",[16,240,241],{},[183,242],{"alt":243,"src":244},".ssh","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F202107092336.png",[16,246,247,248,251],{},"接下來打開 ",[20,249,250],{},"id_ed25519.pub"," 檔案應該會獲得一大推好像亂碼的東西，把裡面疑似亂碼的東西全選複製起來，然後打開 GitHub 到 Setting：",[16,253,254],{},[183,255],{"alt":256,"src":257},"Setting","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F202107092339.png",[16,259,260],{},"然後在側邊欄找到「SSH and GPG keys」：",[16,262,263],{},[183,264],{"alt":265,"src":266},"SSH and GPG keys","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F202107092341.png",[16,268,269],{},"這個頁面上方有一個 SSH keys，旁邊有一個按鈕「New SSH key」用力的點下去！",[16,271,272],{},[183,273],{"alt":274,"src":275},"New SSH key","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F202107092343.png",[16,277,278],{},"(為了寫這一篇我還特別刪除自己的 SSH key QQ)",[16,280,281,282,285,286,289],{},"接下來會跳到一個 Add new 頁面，",[20,283,284],{},"title"," 基本上可以隨你填寫，通常我會填自己的電腦名稱，而底下 ",[20,287,288],{},"key"," 就填你剛剛的公鑰：",[16,291,292],{},[183,293],{"alt":294,"src":295},"Add SSH Key","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F202107092346.png",[16,297,298],{},"填寫完畢之後可能會要你輸入帳號\u002F密碼，輸入完畢之後你就可以在原本的 SSH keys 頁面看到新增進去囉",[16,300,301],{},[183,302],{"alt":303,"src":304},"新增成功","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F202107092347.png",[12,306,308],{"id":307},"測試-ssh","測試 SSH",[16,310,311,312,315],{},"基本上到這邊你就做完了，可是你會發現鑰匙並沒有亮起來，因此你就挑選你任何一個私密專案，然後採用 SSH 的方式 ",[20,313,314],{},"git clone"," 下來試試看",[16,317,318],{},[183,319],{"alt":320,"src":321},"SSH 模式","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F202107092351.png",[16,323,324],{},"如果可以正常 clone 下來就代表你成功啦~",[16,326,327],{},"而且剛剛的 SSH key 頁面上的鑰匙也會亮起來，代表已經被使用且正常運作中：",[16,329,330],{},[183,331],{"alt":332,"src":333},"正常運作","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FGit\u002F202107092353.png",[16,335,336,337,340],{},"另一種測試方式則是輸入 ",[20,338,339],{},"ssh -T git@github.com","，如果成功的話就會得到以下訊息：",[63,342,344],{"className":65,"code":343,"language":67,"meta":68,"style":68},"Hi hsiangfeng! You've successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.\n",[20,345,346],{"__ignoreMap":68},[72,347,348],{"class":74,"line":75},[72,349,343],{},[16,351,352],{},"如果發生錯誤的話，建議你可以試著重新再跑一次流程哩",[12,354,355],{"id":355},"參考文獻",[93,357,358,363],{},[96,359,360],{},[50,361,148],{"href":145,"rel":362},[147],[96,364,365],{},[50,366,369],{"href":367,"rel":368},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.cnblogs.com\u002Fgreencollar\u002Fp\u002F14363535.html",[147],"Ed25519 算法介绍",[371,372,373],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":68,"searchDepth":201,"depth":201,"links":375},[376,377,378,379,380,381,382],{"id":14,"depth":201,"text":14},{"id":26,"depth":201,"text":33},{"id":57,"depth":201,"text":58},{"id":135,"depth":201,"text":136},{"id":222,"depth":201,"text":223},{"id":307,"depth":201,"text":308},{"id":355,"depth":201,"text":355},"Git","2021-07-09 22:43:03","GitHub 除了使用 https 模式連接\u002F上傳之外，也可以使用 ssh 的方式，但是 ssh 的方式比較複雜一點，所以寫一篇紀錄一下。","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fgit\u002Fssh-github-ed25519","3",{"title":6,"description":385},false,"Git\u002F使用-SSH-連接-上傳到你的-GitHub-Ed25519",[396,383,397],"GitHub","ssh key",null,"\u002Fgit\u002F20210709\u002F1381487661\u002F","JvAiy-1YfLWpfKp9YAWSvKq-CmkW8-BQ9ko1rCruBYY",{"newer":402,"older":406},{"url":403,"title":404,"date":405},"\u002Flearnexp\u002F20210710\u002F1926104502\u002F","創造被動收入之前的準備與理財入門","2021-07-10 10:28:14",{"url":407,"title":408,"date":409},"\u002Fvscode\u002F20210709\u002F4359299\u002F","VSCode 自動修正 ESLint 錯誤","2021-07-09 09:41:16",[411,416,421],{"url":412,"title":413,"date":414,"readingMinutes":415},"\u002Fgit\u002F20260226\u002F799954596\u002F","取代 git push --force 更好的方式，git push --force-with-lease","2026-02-26 09:39:40","4",{"url":417,"title":418,"date":419,"readingMinutes":420},"\u002Fgit\u002F20260122\u002F21277993\u002F","Git init 出現 master 分支提示？教你設定預設分支為 main","2026-01-22 16:20:40","2",{"url":422,"title":423,"date":424,"readingMinutes":415},"\u002Fgit\u002F20260121\u002F2025687513\u002F","Git Worktree 是什麼？一個專案同時跑多個 AI Agent 的秘訣","2026-01-21 16:04:27",1784013081322]